06:50.790 --> 06:52.170
No, no. Green light.

06:53.460 --> 06:55.959
Just wondering who this new Tyrone is.

06:55.960 --> 06:57.790
Who's to say this isn't the real me?

07:11.880 --> 07:13.920
<i>There's something
about fear that pushes me.</i>

07:16.120 --> 07:17.500
