07:24.040 --> 07:26.539
It's kinda like your
darkest fear is playing out.

07:26.540 --> 07:28.829
Has this ever happened to you before me?

07:28.830 --> 07:31.789
Yeah. One time with my mom.

07:31.790 --> 07:33.540
And before that.

07:34.620 --> 07:36.620
I think the guy who killed my brother.

07:38.620 --> 07:39.580
