11:25.970 --> 11:27.139
Be a victim.

11:27.140 --> 11:28.640
Remember how I got this from you?

11:30.100 --> 11:31.519
Yeah.

11:31.520 --> 11:32.729
Yeah, you lied to me.

11:32.730 --> 11:34.429
I didn't just lie.

11:34.430 --> 11:36.729
<i>I constructed a narrative</i>

11:36.730 --> 11:38.469
<i>that made you feel safe.</i>

11:38.470 --> 11:40.019
