that went haywire.

12:41.810 --> 12:43.639
Yeah. I know it.

12:43.640 --> 12:45.599
Well, anyway, ROXXON, they, uh...

12:45.600 --> 12:48.099
They closed the case on it,
but they didn't let it die.

12:48.100 --> 12:49.639
