14:00.350 --> 14:03.599
Yeah, um, somebody
stole my bike on Carrolton.

14:03.600 --> 14:05.430
- I got pictures.
- Stolen bike.

14:07.390 --> 14:09.519
Yeah, by the Rue de la Course.

14:09.520 --> 14:10.679
